                    <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white" id="join-heading">Get shipment. Avoid supplement.</h2>
                    <p class="text-lg text-white">Gourier opens new opportunities to obtain your shipments for cheaper and faster.</p>
                    <a class="block w-full py-3 px-5 text-center bg-white border border-transparent rounded-md shadow-md text-base font-medium text-indigo-700 hover:bg-gray-50 sm:inline-block sm:w-auto" href="#">Learn more</a>
                </div>
            </div>
