    </div>
</div>


<div class="bg-white py-24 sm:py-32 lg:py-40">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="sm:text-center">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold leading-8 text-indigo-600">Our features</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">A better way to shop online</p>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">Gourier makes easy to shop worldwide.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-20 max-w-lg sm:mx-auto md:max-w-none">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-y-16 md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-x-12 md:gap-y-16">
        <div class="relative flex flex-col gap-6 sm:flex-row md:flex-col lg:flex-row">
          <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-indigo-500 text-white sm:shrink-0">
            <!-- Heroicon name: outline/globe-alt -->
            <svg class="h-8 w-8" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 008.716-6.747M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 01-8.716-6.747M12 21c2.485 0 4.5-4.03 4.5-9S14.485 3 12 3m0 18c-2.485 0-4.5-4.03-4.5-9S9.515 3 12 3m0 0a8.997 8.997 0 017.843 4.582M12 3a8.997 8.997 0 00-7.843 4.582m15.686 0A11.953 11.953 0 0112 10.5c-2.998 0-5.74-1.1-7.843-2.918m15.686 0A8.959 8.959 0 0121 12c0 .778-.099 1.533-.284 2.253m0 0A17.919 17.919 0 0112 16.5c-3.162 0-6.133-.815-8.716-2.247m0 0A9.015 9.015 0 013 12c0-1.605.42-3.113 1.157-4.418" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="sm:min-w-0 sm:flex-1">
            <p class="text-lg font-semibold leading-8 text-gray-900">Global</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Hundreds of gouriers - courier travelers - transfer your packages from all across the globe to your home.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative flex flex-col gap-6 sm:flex-row md:flex-col lg:flex-row">
          <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-indigo-500 text-white sm:shrink-0">
            <!-- Heroicon name: outline/scale -->
            <svg class="h-8 w-8" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 3v17.25m0 0c-1.472 0-2.882.265-4.185.75M12 20.25c1.472 0 2.882.265 4.185.75M18.75 4.97A48.416 48.416 0 0012 4.5c-2.291 0-4.545.16-6.75.47m13.5 0c1.01.143 2.01.317 3 .52m-3-.52l2.62 10.726c.122.499-.106 1.028-.589 1.202a5.988 5.988 0 01-2.031.352 5.988 5.988 0 01-2.031-.352c-.483-.174-.711-.703-.59-1.202L18.75 4.971zm-16.5.52c.99-.203 1.99-.377 3-.52m0 0l2.62 10.726c.122.499-.106 1.028-.589 1.202a5.989 5.989 0 01-2.031.352 5.989 5.989 0 01-2.031-.352c-.483-.174-.711-.703-.59-1.202L5.25 4.971z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="sm:min-w-0 sm:flex-1">
            <p class="text-lg font-semibold leading-8 text-gray-900">No border fees</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Gourier makes sure that your products do not interfere with VAT of state.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative flex flex-col gap-6 sm:flex-row md:flex-col lg:flex-row">
          <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-indigo-500 text-white sm:shrink-0">
            <!-- Heroicon name: outline/bolt -->
            <svg class="h-8 w-8" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="sm:min-w-0 sm:flex-1">
            <p class="text-lg font-semibold leading-8 text-gray-900">Instant transfers</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Shipment duration is record low because of decentralized gourier network.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative flex flex-col gap-6 sm:flex-row md:flex-col lg:flex-row">
          <div class="flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-indigo-500 text-white sm:shrink-0">
            <!-- Heroicon name: outline/device-phone-mobile -->
            <svg class="h-8 w-8" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 1.5H8.25A2.25 2.25 0 006 3.75v16.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25h7.5A2.25 2.25 0 0018 20.25V3.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H13.5m-3 0V3h3V1.5m-3 0h3m-3 18.75h3" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="sm:min-w-0 sm:flex-1">
            <p class="text-lg font-semibold leading-8 text-gray-900">Mobile notifications</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">You are up to date with push up notifications.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


